name: Normal - BACK
description: Normal is a 9 pieces artwork that I create to embrace and appreciate my body insecurity. I hope this artwork could give a little comfort for everyone who experience the same thing as me. I know that you've been criticizing yourself for god knows how long and I just want you to try approving yourself and you'll see how big the power of self-love is. I went through that too and there's nothing to be worried about because it's Normal.
